    "description": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >引人入胜的主线故事</h2></strong><br><br><br>《吹叶男》是一款的街机动作游戏。你可以漫无目的地把落叶从街头吹到街尾，惹恼邻居后还能获得分数！戏剧性的故事情节将引导进入各种环境，接受不同挑战——说不定你还能拯救全人类？<br><br>重玩短战役获得更多分数，更快通关！你能成为最优秀的吹叶人吗？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212110/extras/9f883dd66bd6b5fba7ceecf63c3530b4.poster.avif?t=1725400607\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212110/extras/9f883dd66bd6b5fba7ceecf63c3530b4.webm?t=1725400607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212110/extras/9f883dd66bd6b5fba7ceecf63c3530b4.mp4?t=1725400607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >击败落叶军团</h2></strong><br><br>除主要战役外，你还可以体验军团模式，在其中与纷至沓来的行军落叶交锋，消灭成千上万的敌人，有策略地获取经验，选择新武器和强化道具，争取撑到最后与落叶之王一决高下。你能推翻秋日的暴君吗？<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212110/extras/47c8c6200d98b8c9a825a1231f93fedb.poster.avif?t=1725400607\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212110/extras/47c8c6200d98b8c9a825a1231f93fedb.webm?t=1725400607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212110/extras/47c8c6200d98b8c9a825a1231f93fedb.mp4?t=1725400607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >没有付费优势</h2></strong><br><br>不必购买任何内容即可畅玩游戏。所有可供购买的其他配套内容均为可选内容，且不会带来任何游戏优势。这是我们恪守的原则。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212110/extras/5676e866658fc8754ab8e11b053ef90d.poster.avif?t=1725400607\" width=60